  { d:0, b:false, en:"Dark Pact: Has been renamed to Dark Bargain.", pl:"Dark Pact: Zmienił nazwę na Dark Bargain." },
  { d:0, b:false, en:"Discharge: Cooldown Time is now 1 second (previously 2 seconds). Now has 15% higher base Damage per Charge removed at all gem levels.", pl:"Discharge: Cooldown Time wynosi teraz 1 s (poprzednio 2 s). Ma teraz 15% wyższe bazowe Damage za każdy usunięty Charge na wszystkich poziomach gemu." },
  { d:0, b:false, en:"Discharge of Misery: Now has 15% higher base Damage per Charge removed at all gem levels.", pl:"Discharge of Misery: Ma teraz 15% wyższe bazowe Damage za każdy usunięty Charge na wszystkich poziomach gemu." },
  { d:0, b:false, en:"Divine Blast: Now deals 42 to 64 Base Off Hand Physical Damage at gem level 1, scaling up to 184 to 276 at gem level 20 (previously 39 to 58 at gem level 1, and 169 to 253 at gem level 20). It now has 2 to 4 Added Physical Damage per 15 Armour on Shield at gem level 1, scaling up to 3 to 6 at gem level 20 (previously 2 to 3 at gem level 1, and 3 to 5 at gem level 20). Now has a base duration of 1.2 seconds (previously 1.5).", pl:"Divine Blast: Zadaje teraz 42–64 Base Off Hand Physical Damage na poziomie gemu 1, rosnąc do 184–276 na poziomie gemu 20 (poprzednio 39–58 na poziomie 1 i 169–253 na poziomie 20). Ma teraz 2–4 Added Physical Damage za każde 15 Armour na Shield na poziomie gemu 1, rosnąc do 3–6 na poziomie gemu 20 (poprzednio 2–3 na poziomie 1 i 3–5 na poziomie 20). Ma teraz base duration 1.2 s (poprzednio 1.5)." },
  { d:0, b:false, en:"Divine Ire: Now has 75% Effectiveness of Added Damage at gem level 20 (previously 50%), and now deals 321 to 482 Physical Damage at gem level 20 (previously 253 to 380).", pl:"Divine Ire: Ma teraz 75% Effectiveness of Added Damage na poziomie gemu 20 (poprzednio 50%) i zadaje teraz 321–482 Physical Damage na poziomie gemu 20 (poprzednio 253–380)." },
  { d:0, b:false, en:"Divine Ire of Disintegration: Now has 140% Effectiveness of Added Damage at gem level 20 (previously 130%), and now deals 623 to 934 Physical Damage at gem level 20 (previously 491 to 737).", pl:"Divine Ire of Disintegration: Ma teraz 140% Effectiveness of Added Damage na poziomie gemu 20 (poprzednio 130%) i zadaje teraz 623–934 Physical Damage na poziomie gemu 20 (poprzednio 491–737)." }
